OL,3,CSummons issued to South West Water
OL,4,Cover parasite outbreak
OL,6,FA summons has been issued to South
OL,7,FWest Water to appear in court after
OL,8,Fthe water supply was contaminated with
OL,9,Fthe parasite cryptosporidium in
OL,10,FBrixham.
OL,12,FUp to 16,000 homes and businesses in
OL,13,Fthe area were told to boil their water
OL,14,Fin May 2024 and the notice was not
OL,15,Flifted until July.
OL,17,FThe Drinking Water Inspectorate has
OL,18,Fordered the water company to appear
OL,19,Fbefore Exeter Magistrates' Court on 2
OL,20,FOctober.
