OL,6,FMarcus Rink, Chief Inspector of the
OL,7,FDrinking Water Inspectorate, has
OL,8,Fstated: "The Brixham incident was
OL,9,Fserious with significant impact on the
OL,10,Fpublic and the wider community.
OL,12,F"Accordingly, I consider it
OL,13,Fappropriate to pass the matter to the
OL,14,Fcourt to consider the evidence in the
OL,15,Fpublic interest."
OL,17,FThe parasite outbreak cost South West
OL,18,FWater nearly #40m, and Caroline
OL,19,FVoaden, the MP for South Devon (which
OL,20,Fincludes Brixham), said she welcomes
OL,21,Fthe summons.
