OL,3,CSummons issued to South West Water
OL,4,Cover parasite outbreak
OL,6,FShe said: "I am pleased to hear that
OL,7,Fthe Drinking Water Inspectorate has
OL,8,Fdecided to take South West Water to
OL,9,Fcourt over the cryptosporidium
OL,10,Foutbreak in Brixham last year.
OL,12,F"It's important we find out exactly
OL,13,Fwhat South West Water knew, and when,
OL,14,Fand why they told people the water was
OL,15,Fsafe to drink when it wasn't.
OL,17,F"Many of my constituents still don't
OL,18,Ftrust the drinking water and are
OL,19,Fpaying for bottled water more than a
OL,20,Fyear on from the outbreak.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
