OL,6,F"This incident affected the whole
OL,7,Fcommunity, damaged businesses, hurt
OL,8,Fthe local economy, and most
OL,9,Fimportantly, made many people severely
OL,10,Fill.
OL,12,F"It's taken a long time to get to this
OL,13,Fpoint, but finally, we are seeing
OL,14,FSouth West Water brought to account."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for South West Water
OL,17,Fsaid: "We will reflect on this summons.
