OL,6,F"South West Water has cooperated fully
OL,7,Fwith the Drinking Water Inspectorate
OL,8,Ffrom the outset of this incident to
OL,9,Fhelp in its investigations.
OL,11,F"We take this incident extremely
OL,12,Fseriously, and we will continue to
OL,13,Fengage fully in response to these
OL,14,Flegal proceedings.
OL,16,F"In the meantime, our focus remains on
OL,17,Fdelivering clean safe drinking water
OL,18,Fto our c.2 million customers across
OL,19,FCornwall, Devon, and the Isles of
OL,20,FScilly."
